+- **Competitor stage artifact schema:** **`CompetitorOutput`** is **`schema_version` 5** (Epic 4 + story 4.4): `run_id`, **`approval_items`**, **`disclosure_items`**, **`pipeline_disclosure_items`** (FR9), **`patent_filing_flags`** (FR10), optional **`competitor_gpt_analysis`** (strategic commentary, threat/opportunity themes, urgent attention flag/items/severity for downstream synthesis), `data_gaps`, `integration_notes`. Legacy **`schema_version` 4** lacked **`competitor_gpt_analysis`**. Older JSON without **`patent_filing_flags`** validates with an empty list. Legacy **`schema_version` 1** was a stub (`note` only).
